    This class is the controller for the login page.

    This class is the controller for the non-admin page.

    This class displays the photo along with its caption and date and time.

    This class defines a picture, which has several attributes, such as caption, tags, date-and-time, etc.
    SearchedPhotosController
    This class is the controller for the screen for searching for photos.
    SearchResultsController
    This class is the controller for the search results screen.
    UserAlbum
    This class is used as a large data structure to store all contents of users, along with their albums and photos.
